"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1934227-Olympic-Games-Paris-Los-Angeles-LA28\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Within the blink of an eye, the ParisOlympic Gamesis on its final day.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 72, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It feels like only yesterday when spectators, athletes and world leaders huddled beneath raincoats duringa soaking wet opening ceremonyon the River Seine.\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past two weeks, spectators have been treated to controversy, tears, disappointments, chaos and numerous shattered world records.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many have been inspired to either take up a new sport or attend the next edition in 2028.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As sports enthusiasts brace themselves for the end of the Games,Express Sportguide you through what you need to know about the next Olympics in four years.\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Where will the next Olympics be held?\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Los Angeles will host the Games for the third time in its history.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999996073484, \"rank\": 2.187052549913386e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Californian city, famous for being home toHollywood's elite, will not be constructing any new permanent venues for the event, reportsthe Mirror.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 721, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Salinas_Californian\", \"score\": 0.9936025701775969, \"rank\": 0.006438620444865818, \"text\": \"The Californian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Salinas_Californian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Salinas_Californian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Olympic events will be held across 80 existing venues, promising one of the most glamorous and glitzy editions of the Games in recent memory.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When are the dates?\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those planning to make the trip for the Games should mark their calendars now.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2028 Games will kick off on July 14 and conclude on July 30.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paralympics will follow hot on the heels of the Olympics, kicking off on August 22 and wrapping up on September 3.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With LA's warm climate and a plethora of glitzy activities, fans can look forward to a sporting extravaganza with a dash of Hollywood glamour.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glamour_(presentation)\", \"score\": 0.999999399367833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood glamour\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glamour_(presentation)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glamour_(presentation)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How to get your hands on tickets?\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently, information about ticket availability and purchase methods is sparse.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If LA follows Paris's ticketing strategy, fans may need to wait until approximately 18 months before the Games commence.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1576, \"end\": 1581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 4.407964285737945e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  For the Paris Games, a ticket lottery was launched 18 months prior to the event, with additional ticket releases closer to the time.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, Milano Cortina, the host of the 2026 Winter Olympics, has recently started selling tickets.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"score\": 0.9999990117255829, \"rank\": 8.982290690758718e-07, \"text\": \"Milano\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\"}, {\"begin\": 2081, \"end\": 2088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 0.9999999901360752, \"rank\": 9.863921794753201e-09, \"text\": \"Cortina\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans can likely anticipate the opportunity to register for the ticket ballot in early 2027.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for pricing, that remains uncertain.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Typically, qualifiers and lesser-known sports offer the most affordable tickets, while finals and high-profile events tend to be pricier.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2575, \"end\": 2588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.899379666382988e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.899379666382988e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"